# .dockerignore — keep secrets + build noise out of the Docker build context (HR-1, §D-002).
# SDD-PROVENANCE: U-004 | vault: .mega-sdd/vaults/api-platform
#
# Excluded: secrets (.env), build output (target/), VCS/IDE state, and host-only
# launchers. KEPT on purpose: .env.example (template, not secret), pom.xml, mvnw,
# mvnw.cmd, .mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.properties (needed by ./mvnw in the builder),
# src/, Dockerfile.

target/
.git/
.gitignore
.mega-sdd/
.idea/
.vscode/
*.log
*.log.*
node_modules/
preview.webp
run-app.sh
docs/
.env
.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar
docker-compose.yml
